--Region is the cluster of data centers

How to chosse an AWS Region?

AWS Availability Zones
--Each region has many AWS Availability Zones (usually 3 min max 6)
--Each zone (AZ) is one or more discrete data centers with redundant power,network 
--They are geo separated

AWS Region
Sydney : ap-southeast-2
Zones
--ap-southeast-2a (data center Alpha , data center Beta)
--ap-southeast-2b (data center Alpha . data center Beta)
--ap-southeast-2c (data center Alpha . data center Beta)


